---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

const seo = {
  title: "Apteczka na Szlaku | Anna Kocaj",
  description:
    "How I designed an app for a real Polish mountain-safety initiative — digitising trailside First Aid Kits to reduce theft and track usage — placing 3rd in a local hackathon.",
  image: "/apetczka_thumbnail.png",
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="mt-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
    <a
      href="/projects"
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-sm mb-8"
    >
      ← Back to projects
    </a>

    <p class="text-sm opacity-50 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 font-medium">
      Case Study · HACKBB 2024
    </p>
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-4 leading-snug">Apteczka na Szlaku</h1>
    <p class="text-lg opacity-70 mb-8 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
      During a local hackathon in Bielsko-Biała, I designed a solution for
      Apteczka na Szlaku, a Polish initiative supporting hikers with First Aid
      Kits.
    </p>

    <!-- Overview grid -->
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 py-6 border-t border-b border-white/10 mb-10"
    >
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">My Role</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">Product Designer</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">
          Timeline
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">24 hours</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">Client</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">Non-profit organization</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-1">Tools</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium">Figma, Adobe Illustrator, Lottie</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero image -->
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
      <Image
        src="/apetczka_thumbnail.png"
        alt="Apteczka na Szlaku app screens"
        width={1200}
        height={675}
        class="w-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHALLENGE -->
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-4">The Challenge</h2>
    <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Apteczka na Szlaku faced theft issues with their First Aid Kits, and
      needed a system to prevent theft and track usage.
    </p>
    <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed">
      The design challenge was to serve two audiences simultaneously: <strong
        >hikers in distress</strong
      > who need to find and use a kit quickly, and <strong
        >trail administrators</strong
      > who need to monitor and manage kit inventory across many locations.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-8">Process</h2>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 font-medium"
        >
          01 — Define
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-base mb-3">
          Two different personas, one product
        </h3>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          The core design tension was that a hiker in an emergency needs a
          simple solution with no login and no learning curve. An administrator
          needs the data, and control. I started by writing down both personas
          needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 font-medium"
        >
          02 — Concept
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-base mb-3">Choosing the best solution</h3>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Our team developed a simple yet effective mobile app solution that
          integrates NFC technology.
          <br />The key features of our solution include:
          <br /><strong>NFC Unlocking:</strong> Users scan their phone to unlock kits
          <br /><strong>Manual Access:</strong> A keypad option for users without
          phones <br /><strong>Usage Tracking:</strong>
          Users report taken items via the app <br /><strong>Navigation:</strong
          > Both AR and standard map navigation to locate kits
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
          <Image
            src="/apetczka_idea.png"
            alt="Apteczka na Szlaku idea"
            width={1200}
            height={675}
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div>
        <p
          class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 mb-2 font-medium"
        >
          03 — Design & Prototype
        </p>
        <h3 class="font-medium text-base mb-3">
          From brief to prototype in a few hours
        </h3>
        <p class="opacity-70 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          I designed the interface and prototype in Figma. Accessibility was a
          priority: the hiker flow needed to work in stressful outdoor
          conditions, so I used high-contrast components, large touch targets,
          and minimal cognitive load.
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden m-6 bg-gray-800">
          <Image
            src="/apteczka_mockups.png"
            alt="Apteczka na Szlaku mockups"
            width={1200}
            height={675}
            class="w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- OUTCOMES -->
    <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-6">Outcomes</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">🏆 3rd</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60">place in a local hackathon</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">🤝 Real</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60">brief from a non-profit organization</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold mb-1">👥 2</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-60">
            user personas needs served in one product
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-gray-800">
        <Image
          src="/IMG_5433.jpg"
          alt="Apteczka na Szlaku mockups"
          width={1200}
          height={675}
          class="w-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- NAVIGATION -->
    <section
      class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16 flex justify-between items-center border-t border-white/10 pt-8"
    >
      <a
        href="/projects/mubu"
        class="opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-sm"
      >
        ← Mubu
      </a>
      <a
        href="/projects/humi"
        class="opacity-50 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity text-sm"
      >
        Next: Humi →
      </a>
    </section>
  </section>

  <style>
    strong {
      color: white;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    em {
      color: inherit;
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
